arly serious enough to warrant his dismissal.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">They were warned that they risked dismissal if the strike continued.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">an employee claim for unfair dismissal</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">his dismissal for poor performance</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"unx\">The court upheld the dismissal.</span></li></ul></span></div><div class=\"collapse\" hclass=\"collapse\" htag=\"div\"><span class=\"unbox\" unbox=\"snippet\" id=\"dismissal_unbox_2\"><span class=\"box_title\">Oxford Collocations Dictionary</span><span class=\"body\"><span class=\"unbox\">adjective</span><ul class=\"collocs_list\"><li class=\"li\">automatic</li><li class=\"li\">immediate</li><li class=\"li\">instant</li><li class=\"li\">…</li></ul><span class=\"unbox\">verb + dismissal</span><ul class=\"collocs_list\"><li class=\"li\">lead to</li><li class=\"li\">call for</li><li class=\"li\">be faced with</li><li class=\"li\">…</li></ul><span class=\"unbox\">preposition</span><ul class=\"collocs_list\"><li class=\"li\">dismissal for</li><li class=\"li\">dismissal on the grounds of</li></ul><span class=\"unbox\">phrases</span><ul class=\"collocs_list\"><li class=\"li\">grounds for dismissal</li><li class=\"li\">reason for dismissal</li></ul><span class=\"xref_to_full_entry\">See <a class=\"Ref\" href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/definition/collocations/dismissal\" title=\" definition in Collocations\n \">full entry</a></span></span></span></div>          \n</li><li class=\"sense\" hclass=\"sense\" sensenum=\"2\" htag=\"li\" ox5000=\"y\" cefr=\"c1\" id=\"dismissal_sng_2\"><span class=\"sensetop\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"sensetop\"><div class=\"symbols\" hclass=\"symbols\" htag=\"div\"><a href=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/wordlists/oxford3000-5000?dataset=english&amp;list=ox5000&amp;level=c1\"><span class=\"ox5ksym_c1\">&nbsp